list.abstract: 《Timing》是一首日语流行歌曲，由徐若瑄演唱，森浩美、ブラックビスケッツ作词，中西圭三、小西贵雄作曲，发行于2011年4月1日，收录于专辑《Natural Beauty》中。
Timing是武汉氪细胞网络技术有限公司开发的一款APP。 2020年12月21日，工信部通报《存在问题的应用软件名单（2020年第七批）》，Timing在列。

yingyinNormal.zh: 时间刚刚好，晚餐刚刚到。

yingyinNormal.en: He's spent months timing testing his monkey face design.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他花数月时间计时和测试猴脸设计。

yingyinNormal.en: What was that I heard? Eric's coming home? Perfect timing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我刚才听到了什么？艾瑞克要回家了？时机刚好。

yingyinNormal.en: You were timing me? Yes. I am going through a bit of a timing phase. How long will it last? We'll find out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在给我计时吗？没错。我最近特别沉迷于计时。这个爱好会持续多久呢？让我们开始计时吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Bad timing. Bernadette just took Cinnamon out for a walk.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真不凑巧，伯纳黛特刚刚带小肉桂出门溜达了。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you having second thoughts? It's just the timing isn't right yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有什么顾虑吗？只是现在时机还不到。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, this is good timing. Remember that Dr. Nowitzki I told you about? She's right here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 时机正好。还记得我之前跟你提过的诺维茨基博士吗？她就在这儿呢。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no, no, no, no, no, no! The DNA matches, the timing works, everything checks out. He is Gusteau's son.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不不不，DNA比对符合，遗嘱尚属有效，一切都没问题，他是食神的儿子。

yingyinNormal.en: We are fighting for our lives here. And when you run, you wanna do so from a position of strength. It's about timing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们现在是在搏命。等你竞选，你会希望处于有利地位，关键在于时机。

yingyinNormal.en: Probably bad timing. Pearson, you called, I came. What's up? Wife and I found out we're having triplets. Oh. I'm sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 时机好像不对。皮尔森，你找我，我就来了。到底什么事？我和我老婆发现我们要生三胞胎了。真遗憾。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello, Peppa and George. That's perfect timing. I've just finished making it. And may we ask what it is? I'll show you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们好啊，佩奇和乔治！你们来得真是时候，正好，我刚刚完成了！我们能知道猪爷爷做的是什么吗？我这就给你们看。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I wouldn't count on it tonight. Doesn't it strike you as, just a little bit of coincidence, the timing of everything?
yingyinNormal.zh: 今晚就别指望了，我这样说会不会打击你？所有事情都这么巧合？

yingyinNormal.en: All right look, if you absolutely have to tell her, at least wait until the timing's right. And that's what deathbeds are for.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不觉得如果你非说不可，至少先等适当的时机再说，所以临终之前才要忏悔。

yingyinNormal.en: You see, Jackie, this is perfect timing. The FEMA plan goes into action, you announce in a couple of weeks, you say you had to run.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你看，杰姬，现在是最佳时机。联邦应急管理局计划开始实施，你几周后宣布参选，说你必须参选。

yingyinNormal.en: It turns out, after multiple studies were analyzed and compared, paper towels came out victorious. Why? A lot of it has to do with timing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 经过多次的研究分析比较，结果竟然是纸巾胜出。为什么呢？其实这和"时间"很有关系。

yingyinNormal.en: There's no resemblance at all. He is not Gusteau's son. Gusteau had no children, and what of the timing of all this? The deadline in the will expires in less than a month!
yingyinNormal.zh: 应该说一点都不像，他不是食神的儿子，食神根本没子嗣，为什么偏偏出现在这时候？距遗嘱继承截止日剩下不到一个月。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
